data.description: STUNNING!! Remodel in sought after Arrowhead Lakes w/ 3 Bed & 2 Baths. VA ASSUMABLE loan potential. Huge Grass common area adjacent to home gives you massive play space that the HOA maintains. Well maintained & up to date features in 2021 along with a Brand New AC unit. Home is located super close to the 101 HWY for easy access to the entire valley. Highly rated Legend Springs Elementary School zone. The home features new quartz counter tops in the kitchen, Ship lap wood feature walls, new flooring, redone master shower, walk-in closets in all 3 bedrooms, vaulted ceilings and a fenced backyard with new astro-turf area and RV gate etc etc. Quiet neighborhood with picturesque walking trails arond the lake. Mountain views from the front yard. Come see it. This one wont last long. Call!!
